<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP21_ProjectGold_HeadAndHeir" s="488447">
  <T n="category">488441<!--TutorialCategory: tutorial_Category_EP21_ProjectGold--></T>
  <T n="name">0x53BF61C7<!--String: "Dynasty Head & Heir"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Dynasty_Heir.png">2f7d0004:00000000:289517c6de8bd5fd</T>
      <T n="text">0xE3E4D1E0<!--String: "The <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dynasty Head</font></b> is the leader of the Dynasty. They are the only one who can make changes to the Values, purchase Perks, assign the Heir, designate Outcasts, and invite or kick Members out of the Dynasty. Their actions and career have an <b><font color='#199C2C'>increased impact</font></b> on Prestige gains or losses compared to other Members, to reflect their status as the leader of the Dynasty. They also benefit from <b><font color='#199C2C'>social advantages</font></b> when interacting with other members of their Dynasty.\n\nThe <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dynasty Heir</font></b> is the next in line for Headship, and will <b><font color='#199C2C'>inherit</font></b> the Head title if the Dynasty Head steps down or passes away. They also experience increased Prestige gains or losses for their actions, as well as social benefits.\n\nA Dynasty Head can choose to change their Heir at any time. Likewise, any Dynasty Member can ask the Head to designate them as Heir if their relationship is strong enough."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Dynasty_Heir2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:812d63ec279c9cd5</T>
      <T n="text">0x12D3A7D6<!--String: "The Dynasty Head keeps their position until they die, lose a challenge, or step down. In order to <b><font color='#199C2C'>step down</font></b>, the Head must select an Heir first. If the Head dies without having an Heir, the next Head will automatically be chosen from among the Members, with preference to the <b><font color='#199C2C'>highest ranking member</font></b> who is neither an Outcast nor younger than a Teen.\n\nIf there are no other Members when the Dynasty Head dies, then the Dynasty ceases to exist."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
